Description:
You arrive at a feline camp, as you approach one of their tents one of them says to you:

"Hello travelers! We are traders and information is our forte. If there is anything you want to know about this desert, you are in the right place.

Of course everything has a price, for 300g we will tell you whatever you want to know".
DescriptionAction: Do you want to buy some information from them?
